                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0786</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9239 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">麦当劳不变，金拱门乍现</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">McDonald&#39;s unchanged, A Deceptive Appearance of Golden Arches</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谭庆美，武娟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">麦当劳</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">麦当劳；金拱门；本土化；特许经营；中信</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">McDonald; Golden Arches; Localization; Franchise; CITIC</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017年10月25日，麦当劳官微发布声明称“麦当劳（中国）有限公司”变更为“金拱门（中国）有限公司”，引发段子手的狂欢。本案例开篇便引出麦当劳（中国）引进战略投资者，成立新公司并引发更名风波；接下来透过现象看本质揭秘网红金拱门，再现麦当劳发家选址以及直营和加盟运营的致富经；描绘了麦当劳全面登陆中国，步步为营，惊喜不断，逐步本土化扩张的27年中国大事记；最后概括了麦当劳与中信完美拍拖进行本土化经营战略转型的荆棘之路。旨在引导学员加深对跨国公司在中国的本土化经营战略转型的理解与认识，也为新时代下跨国公司本土化经营提供良好借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">At the end of October 2017，McDonald&#39;s official micro-blog issued the company name of McDonald&#39;s China headquarters to &quot;Golden Arches (China) Co., Ltd.&quot; This case first describe the import of of strategic investors to achieve cross-border management of McDonald. Then this case describes the secret of the Internet Argumentative Golden Arches, the story of the McDonald&#39;s fortune, store location and different operation mode, The Chinese memorabilia of the 27 years of gradual locatlization expansion. Finally this case introduces the strategic operation of McDonald and CITIC. The purpose of this case is guide students to seek a deep-rooted understanding of the implementation of the localization strategy of foreign enterprises in china. It can also provide a reference for multinational firms to implement the localization operation in the new era.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《 战略管理》、《跨国公司经营与管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业本土化经营战略转型、特许经营</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
